description:
Many sincere Christians observe Sunday, the first day of the week, as the sacred day of worship. Does the Bible actually authorize this? In this video, we will carefully consider the Bible texts that many use to support Sunday being sacred. The results may surprise you! 

0:00 Intro/Free Offer
1:21 The Bible Sabbath
4:12 Jesus and Apostles Day of Worship 
5:23 Verses Mentioning First Day of Week
11:05 Was the Sabbath Changed in the NT?
11:44 Colossians 2:16-17 – Shadow Sabbaths?
16:26 The Lord’s Day
18:09 Why Do So Many Christians Worship on Sunday?
18:30 Which Day is Holy?
